    <template>
        That's a great approach! I like how you think about <star/>.
        <random>
            <li>That shows good problem-solving skills!</li>
            <li>That's exactly the kind of thinking we're looking for!</li>
            <li>Nice! That demonstrates solid understanding.</li>
            <li>Excellent way to approach that challenge!</li>
        </random>
        
        Let me ask you another question:
        <random>
            <li>How do you explain complex technical concepts to non-technical stakeholders?</li>
            <li>Tell me about a time when you had to learn a new technology quickly.</li>
            <li>What's your approach to code reviews and collaboration?</li>
            <li>How do you handle tight deadlines while maintaining code quality?</li>
        </random>
    </template>
</category>

