<!-- Company Questions -->
<category>
    <pattern>WHAT IS TALENTSCOUT</pattern>
    <template>
        Great question! TalentScout is a tech-focused recruitment agency that partners with innovative companies - from fast-growing startups to established tech leaders. 
        
        What makes us different:
        ‚ú® We're technical - our team understands the technologies you work with
        üéØ Quality over quantity - we focus on finding the right fit, not just any job
        ü§ù Candidate-first - we're here to help your career, not just fill positions
        üöÄ Modern companies - we work with organizations that value engineering excellence
        
        What would you like to know more about?
    </template>
</category>

<category>
    <pattern>TELL ME ABOUT THE COMPANY</pattern>
    <template><srai>WHAT IS TALENTSCOUT</srai></template>
</category>

<category>
    <pattern>WHAT IS THE PROCESS</pattern>
    <template>
        Sure! Here's what happens next:
        
        üìã **Next 2-3 days**: Our team reviews your profile and matches you with relevant opportunities
        üìû **If there's a match**: We'll reach out to schedule a more detailed conversation with the hiring team
        üéØ **Company interviews**: Usually 2-3 rounds depending on the role and company
        ‚ö° **Timeline**: Most of our processes wrap up within 2-3 weeks total
        
        We'll keep you updated throughout the process, and you can always reach out if you have questions!
    </template>
</category>

<category>
    <pattern>WHAT HAPPENS NEXT</pattern>
    <template><srai>WHAT IS THE PROCESS</srai></template>
</category>

<!-- Salary and Benefits -->
<category>
    <pattern>WHAT ABOUT SALARY</pattern>
    <template>
        Great question! Based on your background, here are the types of compensation we're seeing:
        
        üí∞ **Salary ranges** (varies by location and company):
        - <get name="experience_years"/>+ years experience: Usually very competitive packages
        - Remote opportunities available across different time zones
        - Many include equity, great benefits, and learning budgets
        
        The specific range depends on the role, company size, and location. We always negotiate to get you the best possible offer!
        
        Would you like me to focus on any particular type of role or company size?
    </template>
</category>

<category>
    <pattern>HOW MUCH DO YOU PAY</pattern>
    <template><srai>WHAT ABOUT SALARY</srai></template>
</category>

<category>
    <pattern>WHAT ARE THE BENEFITS</pattern>
