    <template>
        No worries at all! That's totally fine - not everyone knows everything, and that's what makes great developers.
        <random>
            <li>How do you typically approach learning new things?</li>
            <li>Tell me about something you learned recently that excited you.</li>
            <li>What's your process when you encounter something unfamiliar?</li>
        </random>
    </template>
</category>

<category>
